snippet.title: Rocket League Season 13 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Rocket League Season 13 Gameplay Trailer! Learn more here: http://rl.gg/Season13

Rocket League Season 13 brings back the vibes of the 90s and early 2000s. Unlock items in Rocket Pass Premium including TWO different Car Bodies: Ace and Primo!

Season 13 is available on December 6th. 

#RocketLeague #RocketLeagueSeason13 #RocketLeagueTrailer
